{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"lf01","text":"Music is a major contributor to my life. I am constantly looking for my next favorite album. I'm one of those nuts that listens to the same thing over and over until I'm sick of it. I track my listening habits to see what I've been enjoying. Here are some of the albums that I have been listening to recently.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"lf02","text":"I track my listening habits to see what I've been enjoying. Here is the music I have been playing recently, split by top albums and top artists.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"lf03","text":"Top Albums","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"lf04","text":"Top Artists","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
